@Node "History"
- v1.0  - Testversion

- v1.1  Stupid bug removed causing crash on OS 2.x.
		Cliargs now supported.

- v1.2  Trashdisplay bug removed, with MMU or FPU the CPUtype was not displayed correctly.
		Supports encrypted files.

- v1.3  Uses own screen

- v1.4	Lazymatching added for improved compression
		Uses only 384Kb speedup
		
